title: 57th Annual Fantasy Extravaganza!!!
itunes:title: 57th Annual Fantasy Extravaganza!!!
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, and Gregg Rosenthal embark on the 57th Annual Fantasy Extravaganza! We start by talking receivers with Matt Harmon (3:42), before NFL Fantasy experts Marcas Grant and Michael F. Florio stop by to discuss dueling picks (22:21). Rotoworld legend Patrick "RotoPat" Daugherty gives us all of his cranky takes (39:47), and we "Establish the Run" with fantasy expert Evan Silva (58:38) before signing off with some fantasy advice from the late great Chris Wessling (1:20:00).

Note: Timecodes Approximate.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
